      width="1200"
      height="1200"
    />
  </div>
  <div class="divider my-0"></div>
  <h3><b>Introducing TOAST-ANCHORS GLOBAL</b></h3>
  <Image
    src="/toastmasters.png"
    class="w-full"
    alt="bailamoz"
    width="1200"
    height="1200"
  />
  <p>
    Drawing inspiration from the successful model of Toastmasters International,
    ToastAnchors Global aims to create a supportive and inclusive environment
    where young minded individuals (of all ages) can flourish. Toast-Anchors
    Global is an innovative and dynamic speaking club specially designed for
    those who aspire to develop their public speaking, communication, and
    leadership skills.
  </p>
  <Image
    src="/tag.png"
    class="w-full"
    alt="bailamoz"
    width="1200"
    height="1200"
  />
  <h6><b>Key Features of Toast-Anchors Global:</b></h6>
  <p>
    Structured Meeting Formats: Toast-Anchors Global meetings will follow a
    structured format similar to Toastmasters, including impromptu speaking
    sessions, prepared speeches, and constructive feedback. Interactive
    Workshops: Regular workshops on public speaking techniques, effective
    communication, and leadership skills, facilitated by experienced mentors and
    professionals. Leadership Opportunities: Opportunities for young minded
    individuals to take on leadership roles within the club, enhancing their
    organizational and management skills. Peer Support and Mentorship: A
    supportive and encouraging environment where young minded individuals can
    share their experiences, provide constructive feedback to peers, and benefit
    from mentorship opportunities. Innovative Speech Formats: Introduction of
    creative speech formats, storytelling sessions, and multimedia presentations
    to nurture diverse forms of expression. Digital Engagement: Integration of
    virtual platforms to facilitate global connectivity, enabling members to
    interact with their peers from different cultures and backgrounds. Community
    Outreach: Initiatives focused on leveraging public speaking skills for
    community service, encouraging young minded individuals to make a positive
    impact through their voices. Celebrating Diversity: Embracing and
    celebrating the diversity of voices and perspectives within the club,
    creating an inclusive space where every young minded individual feels valued
    and heard.
  </p>

  <h6><b>Why Toast-Anchors Global? </b></h6>
  <p>
    Toast-Anchors Global aspires to be a beacon of empowerment for young minded
    individuals, equipping them with the skills and mindset needed to become
    articulate communicators, empathetic leaders, and catalysts for positive
    change in their communities and the world. To join us email us at
    celebrate@veeanta.com
  </p>
